page.title: 13MISS RACHAEL LEES
page.content: There is a lady in our village who everyone likes,especially the children.Miss LEES has been living in HINSTOCK for 52 years .She is very popular with the girls because she runs a small riding school.she has three ponies of her own and has four others that she looks after. Children go to her from miles around for lessons. Miss LEES runs the church choir . She has been in the choir for forty years and choirmistress for over twenty years.she has also taught sunday school.Miss LEES is very keen to keep HINSTOCK a nice place to live, she looks after the wild life and helps to manage thirty acres of trees.The wood is now a site of special scientific Interest.
